        'assert-in': [
            'Pool www (dynamic): 47/55 reqs waiting for a free process in listen queue (85.5%) [WARNING], "max children" was reached at least once [WARNING], 42 slow reqs have hit the configured `request_slowlog_timeout` [CRITICAL], 129.1K connections, 23 processes (3 active, 20 idle), Up 3h 28m (since 2021-05-08 09:18:11)',
